001package io.jstach.rainbowgum.annotation;
002
003import static java.lang.annotation.ElementType.TYPE;
004import static java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy.SOURCE;
005
006import java.lang.annotation.Documented;
007import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
008import java.lang.annotation.Target;
009
010/**
011 * API documentation marker that the enum or sealed type may add new case values on
012 * feature release and thus external API consumers desiring backward compatibility should
013 * have a <code>default</code> case.
014 */
015@Documented
016@Retention(SOURCE)
017@Target(TYPE)
018public @interface CaseChanging {
019
020}
